high_descs: Turn around go straight turn right walk to the countertop in the kitchen.
Take the ladle near to the sink
Put the spoon in the sink, pour the water, and take the spoon back.
Turn right go straight then turn right to the cabinet.
Place the ladle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Take the ladle near to the sink clean it and Place it in the cabinet

high_descs: to take the ladle in the kitchen table
Put the spatula in the sink, clean the spatula off.
Take back the spatula in the cabinet.
Place the ladle on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Take the ladle, clean the ladle, place the ladle on the cabinet.

high_descs: Exit from the room, turn right, go straight, turn left again, turn right to the countertop.
Pick up the ladle from the table.
Turn left to turn right side move to the spoon.
Take the spoon from the cabinet and turn around it.
Keep the ladle along with the spoon on the wooden cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Keep the ladle along with the spoon on the cabinet.
